nd initiative, among others. To the extent that these qualities become operative in the therapeutic relation, they provide the effective basis for a strong therapeutic alliance, which plays an essential structuring role at every step of the analytic process.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aMedical personnel and patient. 0aPluralism. 0aPsychoanalysis. 0aPsychoanalytic interpretation. 7aPSYCHOLOGY / Movements / Psychoanalysis.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press eBook-Package Archive Pre-2000z978311053801440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030014630140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300146301423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300146301/original  a978-3-11-053801-4  Yale University Press eBook-Package Archive Pre-2000b2000  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles